on iOS for you to choose from.

00:24:32.270 --> 00:24:36.600
If you need to,
you can also embed fonts in your book.

00:24:36.640 --> 00:24:42.500
And then, iBooks supports both
OpenType and TrueType fonts.

00:24:42.700 --> 00:24:45.900
Also, if needed, you can use something
called font mangling.

00:24:46.070 --> 00:24:50.820
Font mangling is a method of font
encryption that's available in EPUB.

