Let me show you how to include it.

00:25:05.110 --> 00:25:06.940
It's super easy.

00:25:07.070 --> 00:25:10.110
A little bit of code because
it's all standard CSS.

00:25:10.680 --> 00:25:13.440
In this example,
we're calling on a system font,

00:25:13.440 --> 00:25:14.310
Heffler text.

00:25:14.320 --> 00:25:17.140
All you need to do is include
the font family with the

00:25:17.140 --> 00:25:18.720
font name you want to use.

00:25:18.720 --> 00:25:24.720
If you want to embed a font,
you want to use this same bit of code,

