00:25:38.850 --> 00:25:43.630
I really encourage you to use fonts
in your books because as you can see,

00:25:43.630 --> 00:25:46.160
you can create some really
great handwritten notes.

00:25:46.170 --> 00:25:48.160
It adds a lot of character to your books.

00:25:48.160 --> 00:25:53.280
But I know that I've also told you
that one of the great things about

00:25:53.510 --> 00:25:58.400
flowing EPUBs is that it gives the
