00:26:07.230 --> 00:26:11.030
the ability to say, "Hey,
these fonts are critical to the

00:26:11.080 --> 00:26:13.120
look of my book and I want you,
iBooks,

00:26:13.120 --> 00:26:18.280
to respect them." So all you have to
